{
  "stem": "12462.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The main thing he did, which I kept repeating in my presentation-- there, I should go back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The British had-- through the British Broadcasting System-- had intercepted all the main speeches that Fritzsche had made as the head of the Reich radio division of the Propaganda Ministry.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fritzsche didn't get that position until after the war began.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then he began making speeches every week, called 'Hans Fritzsche Spricht,' Hans Fritzsche Speaks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And these were listened to, and a lot of propaganda in them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These had been intercepted and parts of them translated-- well, they were translated into English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, strangely enough, the British had destroyed the discs, because they needed them for other transcriptions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had the translations, but not the originals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We put out notices throughout Germany and tried to see if anybody had these.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nothing came of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Later on, in a later trial, a German did turn them in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He'd kept copies of these things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we didn't have them in the first trial.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to introduce [CHUCKLES] German translations for the-- from the English, of-- which was not the original document, which kind of weakened the thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he didn't challenge that too much, because they-- we had so many of them that were so much the same thing, that he decided-- his counsel, whose name was Fritz, Dr.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fritz, decided that he wouldn't challenge them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When some of these documents were put through the defense center [CLEARS THROAT] into the hands of the defense counsel, long before the Fritzsche case came up, Dr.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fritz, his defense counsel, asked to see me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came in, and I showed him some of the documents we were going to use.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
